@startuml Asset Link Management Business Process
title Asset Link Management Business Process

participant "Camunda" as C
participant "Kong" as K
participant "AssetLink\nMicroservice" as A
database "AWS RDS" as DB
queue "Kafka\nCluster" as KF
participant "Telemetry\nMicroservice" as T

C -> K : Create Request
K -> A : Forward Request
A -> DB : INSERT AssetLink
DB --> A : OK
A --> K : Response (AssetLinkID)
K --> C : Forward Response

C -> KF : Create topic\n"AssetLinkID-UtilityOperator"
note right of C: via Camunda Kafka Connector
KF --> C : Topic created OK

C -> K : Activate consumer for new topic (REST)
K -> T : Forward request
activate T
T -> KF : Subscribe to topic\nAssetLinkID-UtilityOperator
KF --> T : Subscribed OK
T --> K : Consumer active
deactivate T
K --> C : Forward Response

note over C, T
  On de-association: revoke security keys,
  stop telemetry consumer, delete topic,
  update aggregate capacity calculations
end note

@enduml
